subject: Marathon Running
New York City Marathon
Running
lead_paragraph: Gete Wami, a 33-year-old Ethiopian woman, won the Berlin Marathon on Sept. 30.  and on Sunday, only five weeks after that race, she will run in the New York City Marathon.
